re examples, grammar exercises, and discussion questions. The textbook also includes a comprehensive pinyin index. A Reflection of Reality will effectively improve students' Chinese language skills and their understanding of today's China.Advanced-level Chinese language textbook Selected short stories reflect contemporary Chinese society and cultureExtensive vocabulary lists, sentence structure examples, grammar exercises, and discussion questionsComprehensive pinyin index  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aChinese languagevReaders. 0aChinese languagevTextbooks for foreign speakersxEnglish. 0aShort stories, Chinesex21st century. 0aShort stories, Chinese. 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / Chinese.2bisacsh1 aChiang, Joanne, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aYu, Liping, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978140085256740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781400852567423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781400852567.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles